text: Michel Saint Lezer (born 31 August 1946) is a French ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:French male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of France Category:Ski jumpers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Haut-Rhin
